3BIt's%20not%20like%20I%20had%20to%20move%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECamilleri's%20patience%20paid%20off%20after%20a%20year%20of%20house%20hunting.%20He%20not%20only%20avoided%20a%20bidding%20war%20%E2%80%94%20he%20landed%20on%20a%20price%20that%20was%20%2425%2C000%20lower%20than%20what%20the%20seller%20was%20originally%20asking.%20He%20paid%20%24670%2C000%20for%20the%202%2C300-square-foot%20home.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20part%20skill%20and%20part%20luck.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20literally%20negotiating%20over%20the%20phone%20and%20making%20sales%20all%20day%20long.%20It's%20what%20I%20do%20for%20a%20living.%20I%20understand%20how%20negotiations%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20knew%20they%20weren't%20going%20to%20accept%20my%20first%20offer%2C%20but%20I%20started%20about%20%2450%2C000%20under%20asking%2C%20then%20they%20came%20back%20with%20a%20little%20bit%20higher%20than%20I%20wound%20up%20paying%2C%20and%20then%20we%20found%20some%20middle%20ground.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20added%20that%20lowballing%20wouldn't%20work%20in%20every%20situation%3A%20%26quot%3BIt%20really%20depends%20on%20the%20demand%20for%20that%20home.%20If%20there%20were%2010%20people%20bidding%20on%20the%20home%2C%20I'm%20sure%20it%20wouldn't%20have%20worked%20out%20in%20my%20favor.%20In%20this%20instance%2C%20I%20do%20actually%20feel%20like%20I%20might%20have%20gotten%20lucky%20because%20it%20is%20a%20beautiful%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20locked%20in%20a%202.875%25%20interest%20rate%2C%20which%20still%20seems%20surprising%20to%20him%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20get%20that%20in%20New%20Jersey.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20though%20his%20rate%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20steal%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bif%20I%20had%20no%20other%20choice%20and%20I%20had%20to%20pay%207%25%2C%20I%20would%20still%20do%20th