d%20tournament%20at%20the%20international%20level!%C2%A0In%20fact%2C%20he%20says%2C%2080%20to%2090%25%20of%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F283750%2Fmir-sultan-khan-first-asian-grandmaster-chess-unsung-genius-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echess%20career%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20involved%20playing%20against%20sighted%20opponents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20only%20child%2C%20Darpan%20was%20born%20in%20Udaipur%2C%20Rajasthan.%20When%20he%20was%20six%20months%20old%2C%20his%20family%20moved%20to%20Gujarat%2C%20where%20his%20father%20wanted%20to%20set%20up%20his%20own%20business%2C%20and%20he%20has%20been%20based%20in%20Vadodara%20ever%20since.%20When%20he%20was%20just%20three%20years%20old%2C%20tragedy%20struck.%20He%20was%20afflicted%20with%20Stevens-Johnson%20Syndrome%2C%20a%20rare%2C%20life-threatening%20condition%2C%20and%20lost%20his%20eyesight%20completely.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20he%20was%20eight%2C%20he%20had%20undergone%2050%20surgeries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENever%20used%20Braille%2C%20thanks%20to%20technology%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20doctors%20gave%20up%20hope%2C%20Darpan%E2%80%99s%20parents%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fvideo%2Fthis-school-is-empowering-underprivileged-youth-by-providing-free-education-meals%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efocus%20on%20his%20education%3C%2Fa%3E.%20His%20father%2C%20who%20runs%20a%20jewellery%20business%2C%20and%20his%20mother%2C%20a%20homemaker%2C%20wanted%20him%20to%20study%20in%20a%20mainstream%20school.%20Many%20schools%20r