irected%20to%20%E2%80%98centres%20of%20excellence%E2%80%99%2C%20spread%20across%20public%20hospitals%20in%20India%2C%20where%20patients%20would%20be%20able%20to%20access%20wherewithal%20for%20treatment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98He%20is%20like%20God%20to%20me%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERekha%20K%20(30)%20was%20featured%20on%20a%20TV%20show%20in%202011%20where%20she%20spoke%20about%20her%20battle%20with%20Mucopolysaccharidosis%20type%20IV%20(MPS%20IV)%2C%20a%20rare%20genetic%20condition%20that%20causes%20bone%20growth%20abnormalities.%20Prasanna%20happened%20to%20be%20watching%20the%20show%20that%20day.%20When%20he%20heard%20Rekha%20detail%20the%20hassle%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F123505%2Fcouple-loses-son-helps-others-with-rare-disease%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccessing%20the%20right%20treatment%20modality%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20show%2C%20requested%20to%20be%20put%20in%20touch%20with%20her%2C%20and%20told%20her%20about%20ORDI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fchangemakers-india-3-1738839855.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Prasanna%20Shirol%20and%20several%20other%20rare%20disease%20advocates'%20fight%20culiminated%20in%20a%20sweet%20victory%20in%202017%20when%20Rs%20100%20crore%20was%20sanctioned%20under%20the%20National%20Rare%20Disease%20Fund%20(NRDF)%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fchangemakers-india-3-1738839855.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fchangemakers-india-3-1738839855-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F